                  </hi>. I am a clerk, in the house of Messrs. Leaf and Co.—this is the book the prisoner had of moneys received—I received the moneys accounted for the 10th of July—he did not account for this 4<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 1<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. nor the 22<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 9<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
